    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n.html-preview .a5 {className: a5; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Эр-хотиннинг умумий мол-мулкидаги улушга бўлган мулк ҳуқуқи тўғрисидаги гувоҳнома бериш ҳақидаги ариза</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ариза келиб тушди: </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Ариза келиб тушган сана</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\">Мерос иши № <span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"\">{#20}Мерос ишининг рақами</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.18282548476px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза берилаётган нотариал идора манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-29 structure-31\" style=\"className:29 31; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; display: none;\">{#29} давлат нотариал идораси рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-29\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; display: none;\">{#29} </span><span class=\"structures structure-29 structure-29\" style=\"className:29 29; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; display: none;\">{#29}сонли давлат нотариал идораси</span><span class=\"structures structure-30 structure-30\" style=\"className:30 30; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#30}хусусий нотариал идора</span><span class=\"structures structure-30\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#30} нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-30 structure-33\" style=\"className:30 33; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#30}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">га </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.18282548476px;\">\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Аризачининг яшаш уйи рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уйда яшовчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Ариза берувчи биринчи тарафининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#32}Ариза берувчи иккинчи тарафининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">лардан</span></p>\n<p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto; font-weight: bold;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Биз – </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Ариза берувчи биринчи тарафининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#32}Ариза берувчи иккинчи тарафининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">лар </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Қонуний никоҳ қайд этилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> кунидан бошлаб қонуний никоҳда яшаб келамиз.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Биргаликдаги никоҳимиз даврида орттирилган маблағларга </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Аризачининг яшаш уйи рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уй-жойни сотиб олиб, уни </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#23}Уй-жойнинг олди-сотди шартномасини тасдиқлаган нотариал идора манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#24}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span class=\"structures structure-35 structure-37\" style=\"className:35 37; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#35} давлат нотариал идораси рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-35\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#35} </span><span class=\"structures structure-35 structure-35\" style=\"className:35 35; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#35}-сонли давлат нотариал идораси</span><span class=\"structures structure-36 structure-36\" style=\"className:36 36; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#36}хусусий нотариал идора</span><span class=\"structures structure-36\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#36} </span><span class=\"structures structure-36 structure-38\" style=\"className:36 38; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#36}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#25}Олди-сотди шартномаси расмийлаштирилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#26}Қайд қилинган реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> реестр рақам билан қайд қилинган олди-сотди шартномасига асосан <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#32}Ариза берувчи иккинчи тарафининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">нинг номига расмийлаштирдик.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси «Нотариат тўғрисида»ги Қонунининг 62-моддасига асосан, никоҳимиз давомида орттирилган умумий мол-мулкка, яъни </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Аризачининг яшаш уйи рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уй-жойга нисбатан ҳар биримизга </span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#27}Уй-жой қисмидан аризачи тарафларга ажратиладиган улуш қисми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> улушга мулк ҳуқуқи тўғрисида гувоҳнома беришингизни сўраймиз.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\">с</p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">ИМЗОЛАР:</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1. Аризачи: _______________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2. Аризачи: _______________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариуснинг тасдиқлов ёзуви.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">Изоҳ:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: italic;\"> ушбу ариза эр ёки хотиннинг бири томонидан ҳам ёзилиши мумкин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n</div></div>",
